# pyTxTchat
### Python Terminal Text Chat 
- using Apache Kafka

### using
```
$ pip install pytxtchat

$ pytxtchat-ping
pong
```

### if you're a developer
```bash
$ git clone ... & cd ...

$ pdm venv create
$ source .venv/bin/activate
$ pdm install

$ pytest --cov
